! Line Numbers for CodeMirror 6

Displays line numbers in the editor gutter and highlights the active line.

!! Features

* ''Line numbers'' — shows line numbers in the left gutter
* ''Active line highlighting'' — highlights the current line
* ''Active gutter highlighting'' — highlights the line number of the current line
* ''Configurable'' — enable/disable each feature independently

!! Configuration

Both features are enabled by default and can be configured via:

* `$:/config/codemirror-6/editor/lineNumbers` — show/hide line numbers
* `$:/config/codemirror-6/editor/highlightActiveLine` — enable/disable active line highlighting

!! API

The plugin adds the following methods to the engine:

* `setLineNumbers(show)` — programmatically show/hide line numbers
* `setHighlightActiveLine(show)` — programmatically enable/disable active line highlighting
